bility extending down to $\\sim \\mu$s timescales,\nthis will provide strong evidence in favor of magnetospheric models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Jul 2020 18:00:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Aug 2020 21:33:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-09"}
