ost half of the initial energies for droplet\nimpact onto thin wall films, and most likely by influencing the capillary time\nscale through damping.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Jul 2020 15:14:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-03"}
